Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that what you're\Nafter isn't in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?! To achieve\Nsomeone else's goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in dying over that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tells others not to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's the first to lay down\Nher own life to save others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you that\Nyou can just ditch that burden...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want her to die!\NThat's how friends are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel proud from the bottom\Nof my heart that I was able
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to serve you, the Nefertari Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Alabasta's guardian deity... Falcon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroys...\Nthe royal family's enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Will Surpass You! Rain Falls In Alabasta!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... protected the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, all of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a close watch on\Nwhere this country ends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is sure to happen\Nto mark the start of a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... aren't they stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please...\N--Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please... stop fighting!\N--You dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! What're you\Njust standing there for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you have to\Npunch or kick! Just stop the rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reduce the number of casualties\Nas much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... the beginning is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day that my enormous ambition starts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want her to die!\NThat's how friends are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we won't quit fighting as long\Nas she doesn't give up on her country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally manage to speak\Nand that's all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bluff that suits you well, a loser\Nwho's about to die any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's even groundless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man who'll be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, brat. The more\Na man knows about this sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the less he'd make such thoughtless remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you that there're\Ntons of rookies like you in this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you learn the level of this sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the more you'll give up\Non having such dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man... who will surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scorpion's poison\Nshould definitely be working...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this brat getting\Nall that strength from...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mr. 5 duo was taken down?\NWho the hell did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy? Never heard of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying they're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pirates are in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a brat who comes\Nfrom who knows where...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just fall along with this\Nsacred temple already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sables...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pesado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...La Spada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable... There's so much\Nbedrock between here and the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look...! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, so much blood will be shed\Nthroughout the kingdom. It'll be a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just return safely! I need\Nto return as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't make it in time, a million\Ncitizens will kill each other pointlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then all we have to do...\Nis beat up that Crocodile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why he flew out\Nfrom such a place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I knew it from\Nthe start! But in any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When our enemy's already gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shed... any more blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Koza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold suspicion, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The madness has stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've begun hesitating...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is clearing up due to the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fight... any more...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi's voice has reached everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vivi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the princess was absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come he fell into a place like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile- "san,"  you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them what he did to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec. Just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain falling right now...\Nwill fall again as it used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since our nightmares are... all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy on your back is\None of ours. I'll take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...! Daddy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Daddy?! Is he Vivi-chan's father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Vivi. Go back to the Square.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! The rebellion has finally stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be proper if the king\Nor princess didn't say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Farewell to Arms!\NPirates and Different Ideas of Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
